   you can convert the card list into a JS array. */
---
<!-- Steps Section -->
<section id="steps" class="steps section">

  <!-- Section Title -->
  <div class="container section-title" data-aos="fade-up">
    <h2>Our Approach</h2>
    <div><span>How Impact Orbit Group</span> <span class="description-title">Delivers Value</span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">

    <div class="steps-wrapper">

      <!-- Step 01 -->
      <div class="step-item" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-delay="200">
        <div class="step-content">
          <div class="step-icon">
            <i class="bi bi-lightbulb"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="step-info">
            <span class="step-number">Step 01</span>
            <h3>Discovery & Insight</h3>
            <p>We start by understanding your challenges, context, and goals across the space ecosystem. This includes sector trends, sustainability opportunities, digital maturity, stakeholder needs, and organisational realities. Insight drives clarity and identifies strategic levers for impact.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 02 -->
      <div class="step-item" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-delay="300">
        <div class="step-content">
          <div class="step-icon">
            <i class="bi bi-gear"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="step-info">
            <span class="step-number">Step 02</span>
            <h3>Strategy & Design</h3>
            <p>Building on insights, we co-create strategies tailored to your objectives—whether that’s digital transformation via Green Orbit Digital, communications and PR campaigns through Green Orbit Space Communications & PR, capability development via Green Orbit Academy, or event-led engagement like Space Impact Forum and Leicester Space Week. Our outputs are structured, evidence-based, and actionable.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 03 -->
      <div class="step-item" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-delay="400">
        <div class="step-content">
          <div class="step-icon">
            <i class="bi bi-bar-chart"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="step-info">
            <span class="step-number">Step 03</span>
            <h3>Implementation & Collaboration</h3>
            <p>We translate strategy into action—developing campaigns, digital systems, communications frameworks, impact models, and events. Across all ventures, collaboration, agility, and measurable progress ensure your organisation achieves tangible outcomes and long-term impact.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 04 -->
      <div class="step-item" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-delay="500">
        <div class="step-content">
          <div class="step-icon">
            <i class="bi bi-check2-circle"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="step-info">
            <span class="step-number">Step 04</span>
            <h3>Review, Learn & Scale</h3>
            <p>We embed learning, optimise approaches, and scale solutions across your initiatives. From sustainability programmes to digital platforms and public engagement events, our focus is on resilience, continuous improvement, and creating lasting positive impact throughout the space ecosystem.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>
<!-- /Steps Section -->